node.text: 5 weeks since gyms have reopened. 5 weeks of consistent training. My weight has increased from 190lb to 207lb within this time frame. Although the gains (especially strength gains) have been nice, this is the heaviest I’ve ever been and so it’s time to up the cardio!🏃🏽‍♂️💨

node.text: Me after being professional all day... who else can relate?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dr. Marco on April 10, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, biceps, beard and indoor.

node.text: Less than 2 weeks to go until my final licensing exam. This exam is what will allow me to transition from being a resident doctor to a board certified family doctor! It all comes down to this one final push! Time to get in my zone and, for one last time, study like people’s lives depend on it!🤓📚💪🏼

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dr. Marco on March 25, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and beard.

node.text: Another 16 hour day in the books💪🏼🏥

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dr. Marco on March 20, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, biceps, beard and indoor.

node.text: I would rather be completely exhausted from the hard times which breed success, than well rested from achieving nothing.

node.text: Waiting for my next patient like...
